Millard Afrael Ayo (born 26 January 1986) is a Tanzanian broadcaster, journalist and blogger. 
Ayo is best known for his Amplifier show on the radio station, Clouds FM. 
He first rose to prominence after joining ITV and Radio One in 2008, before leaving in 2010 for Clouds FM. Ayo has also launched his own website at one point. 
In addition, Millard has a YouTube channel called Ayo TV, which provides journalism and acts like an internet TV.[1] 
Ayo has been widely reputed in East Africa for providing information considered timely of events on politics, sports and entertainment. 
